title: Orion to star in Rathmines air show
text:
Orion to star in Rathmines air show 
Newcastle Herald Friday 23rd October, 2015 
THE Rathmines Catalina Festival will not be reverberating with the distinctive roar of a Catalina for the first time in recent years, but organisers say there are still plenty of reasons to pay homage to one of the most important Australian bases during World War II....
